title: Glee: The Ultimate Fourth Season
description:
The complete fourth season of Glee, with all 22 episodes.

1. The New Rachel
2. Britney 2.0
3. Makeover
4. The Break-Up
5. The Role You Were Born to Play
6. Glease
7. Dynamic Duets
8. Thanksgiving
9. Swan Song
10. Glee, Actually
11. Sadie Hawkins
12. Naked
13. Diva
14. I Do
15. Girls (and Boys) on Film
16. Feud
17. Guilty Pleasures
18. Shooting Star
19. Sweet Dreams
20. Lights Out
21. Wonder-ful
22. All or Nothing

This package also includes the CDs released throughout season 4, including Season 4 Volume 1, The Christmas Album Volume 3, Glease, and Britney 2.0.

As an added bonus, in separate episode folders, I have included the original versions of the songs featured on Glee. This is something I do myself.
